                    <td style="padding-bottom: 40px;padding-bottom: 40px;text-align:left">
                        <p style="color:#333333;"><strong>Singapore, July 1, 2019 – StarNgage, the influencer marketplace connecting brands with influential content creators, has announced the launch of new AI-powered influencer profile analytics (Influencer Profile Analytics 3.0).</strong></p>
                        <p style="padding-top: 20px;">The new updates enables marketers to identify <strong>Mega, Macro, Micro</strong> and <strong>Nano influencers</strong> on Instagram. With the launch of StarNgage Influencer Profile Analytics 3.0, marketers can now access to one of the most comprehensive databases of influencers and select the right influencer to work with, based on their insights and audience persona. They can also learn how the influencer has performed in the past, before selecting the most relevant candidate. By accessing StarNgage Influencer Profile Analytics directly on StarNgage marketplace, marketers can shorten their marketing cycle through an <strong>all-in-one</strong> influencer marketing solution, from influencer <strong>discovery, selection, hiring, payment</strong> to <strong>reporting</strong>. The marketplace has successfully matched influencers with over <strong>1,500</strong> campaigns regionally.</p>
                        <p style="text-align: center; padding-top: 30px;padding-bottom: 30px"><img src="https://starngage.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/influencer-profile-analytics-content.jpg" style="max-width:100%;"></p>
                        <p>StarNgage Influencer Profile Analytics is available as a standalone feature for <strong>$0.99</strong> per profile and marketers can sign up and purchase via credit card on <a href="https://starngage.com/" target="_blank">StarNgage.com</a></p>
                        <div style="text-align: center; line-height: 150%; color: #333333; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; padding: 30px; font-weight: bold;"><a style="text-decoration: none; color: #fff; background-color: #ed7633; padding: 15px 30px; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block;" href="https://starngage.com/app/global/sso/advertiser-sign-up" target="_blank" rel="noopener">SIGN UP AND PURCHASE NOW!</a></div>
                        <p>With StarNgage Influencer Profile Analytics, marketers can search by location, age, gender , topic of influence and target audience demographic. Marketers can also dig into influencer posts for inspiration and explore their average number of likes, number of engagement, brands they’ve worked with before, and how they performed in the past to make an informed decision. StarNgage influencers profile database is one of the most well-profiled on the market, with more than 1.5 million Instagram Influencer profiles which have 1000+ followers.</p>
